section.section:
"Ballot" or "official ballot" includes:
an absentee ballot;
a provisional ballot;
a document ballot; or
a voting machine ballot.

text.section:
"Political action committee" means a political committee that is not:
a political party;
a central committee;
a slate;
a political committee organized and operated solely to support or oppose a single candidate; or
a political committee organized and operated solely to support or oppose a ballot issue.
